---
import Site from '../layouts/Site.astro';
import DeployButton from '../components/DeployButton.astro';
---

<Site title="Docs — nodrix" description="Post-deploy setup, device protocol, and read API reference.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Setup</h1>

    <section class="mt-8 space-y-4">
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
        Deploy the platform to your Cloudflare account, then create the first account to claim ownership.
      </p>
      <DeployButton />
    </section>

    <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">1. Claim the deployment</h2>
    <ol class="mt-3 list-decimal space-y-2 pl-6 text-sm text-neutral-700">
      <li>Open your worker URL (e.g. <code class="font-mono">nodrix.workers.dev</code>).</li>
      <li>Register the first account with email and password — it's auto-assigned the <strong>owner</strong> role and a default project is created.</li>
      <li>(Optional) In <strong>Settings → Sign-in providers</strong>, add Google or GitHub OAuth client credentials to enable social sign-in.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">2. Register a device</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
      In the admin UI → <strong>Devices</strong> → <strong>Create</strong>. The token is shown
      once — copy it into your device firmware now.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">3. Device protocol</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
      Three HTTPS endpoints. Auth: <code class="font-mono">Authorization: Bearer &lt;device_token&gt;</code>.
    </p>
    <pre class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-neutral-900 p-4 text-xs text-neutral-100"><code>POST /v1/telemetry
{`{ "ts": 1715900000, "metrics": { "temperature": 23.4, "humidity": 61 } }`}
&rarr; 204 No Content

GET /v1/commands
&rarr; {`{ "commands": [ { "id": "cmd_x", "name": "relay", "value": "on" } ] }`}

POST /v1/commands/ack
{`{ "ids": ["cmd_x"] }`}
&rarr; {`{ "acked": 1 }`}</code></pre>

    <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">4. Read API</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
      For external apps. Mint a token in the admin UI → <strong>API tokens</strong>.
      Auth: <code class="font-mono">Authorization: Bearer &lt;user_token&gt;</code>.
    </p>
    <pre class="mt-4 overflow-x-auto rounded-md bg-neutral-900 p-4 text-xs text-neutral-100"><code>GET /v1/projects/:proj/devices
GET /v1/projects/:proj/devices/:id/state          (edge-cached, ~1s)
GET /v1/projects/:proj/devices/:id/series?metric=temperature&window=1h</code></pre>
  </main>
</Site>
